Interface FieldCodec<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - encoded type
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FieldCodec.BooleanArrayFieldCodec, FieldCodec.BooleanFieldCodec, FieldCodec.ByteArrayFieldCodec, FieldCodec.ByteFieldCodec, FieldCodec.CharArrayFieldCodec, FieldCodec.CharFieldCodec, FieldCodec.DoubleArrayFieldCodec, FieldCodec.DoubleFieldCodec, FieldCodec.FloatArrayFieldCodec, FieldCodec.FloatFieldCodec, FieldCodec.Impl, FieldCodec.IntegerArrayFieldCodec, FieldCodec.IntegerFieldCodec, FieldCodec.LongArrayFieldCodec, FieldCodec.LongFieldCodec, FieldCodec.ObjectArrayFieldCodec, FieldCodec.ObjectFieldCodec, FieldCodec.ShortArrayFieldCodec, FieldCodec.ShortFieldCodec

    public interface FieldCodec<E>
    A FieldCodec encapsulates encoding a field to an encoded type E, and vice-versa.
